{"arkId":"cl010099475","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010099475","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Montre ovale","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre ovale"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Henri IV (1589-1610) (Occident-\u003ERenaissance-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons) ; Louis XIII (1610-1643) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1600 - 1625","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 531 - Paul Garnier, Vitrine 2","room":"Salle 531, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1600,"endYear":1625,"imprecision":"","text":"1er quart du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Martinot, Denis","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 7029","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Montre ovale ; bo\u00eetier form\u00e9 de deux couvercles mont\u00e9s \u00e0 charni\u00e8re. L\u0027un en argent poli contient un cadran solaire et une boussole (aiguille manquante) ; style grav\u00e9 et reperc\u00e9 de rinceaux. L\u0027autre, prot\u00e9geant le cadran, est en cristal de roche. Carrure orn\u00e9e d\u0027une frise grav\u00e9e de rinceaux anim\u00e9s de sc\u00e8nes : un chien poursuivant un sanglier ; un berger et son chien gardant un troupeau. Pendant en forme de chapiteau ; bouton piriforme en vis-\u00e0-vis. Plaque du cadran grav\u00e9e de rinceaux fleuris peupl\u00e9s d\u0027Amours, d\u0027oiseaux, d\u0027\u00e9cureuils ; au centre figure un oiseleur tendant ses filets d\u0027apr\u00e8s une gravure d\u0027E. Delaune. Anneau horaire rapport\u00e9 \u00e0 chiffres romains. Echappement \u00e0 verge, fus\u00e9e avec corde \u00e0 boyau. Coq et cliquet ajour\u00e9s et grav\u00e9s de rinceaux \u00e0 fleurs de fraisier.","inscriptions":"Signature : \r ; mouvement sign\u00e9 : D\/Martinot\/AParis","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"7","displayDimension":"7 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"3,6","displayDimension":"3,6 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"2,4","displayDimension":"2,4 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : argent\r\nMat\u00e9riau : cristal de roche\r\nMat\u00e9riau : laiton","placeOfCreation":"Paris (France-\u003EIle-de-France = Ile de France)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection Gavet ; collection Paul Garnier (1834-1916), \u00e0 Paris. Don Paul Garnier, en 1916.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"M. Garnier, Paul ","note":"","role":", Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date du d\u00e9cret","value":"19\/06\/1916","startYear":1916,"endYear":1916}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"don"}],"period":[{"value":"Henri IV (1589-1610)"},{"value":"Louis XIII (1610-1643)"}],"place":[{"value":"Paris"}],"objectType":[{"value":"horlogerie"},{"value":"montre"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"RMN, Mus\u00e9e du Louvre (dir.), Un temps d\u0027exub\u00e9rance. Les arts d\